Interface MeterReadingRepositoryCustom

All Known Subinterfaces:
MeterReadingRepository
All Known Implementing Classes:
MeterReadingRepositoryImpl
public interface MeterReadingRepositoryCustom
Custom repository interface for MeterReading entities.

Defines custom query methods that are not part of the standard MeterReadingRepository interface. Implementations of this interface provide the logic for these custom methods.
